 {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1733731195", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1733731195", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 71391, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1733731195", "stars": 9701, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 811316, "username": "Lcy0128", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Lcy0128", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f7e4/22ec/811316_mini.png?m=1778739851", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f7e4/22ec/811316_normal.png?m=1778739851", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f7e4/22ec/811316_large.png?m=1778739851", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f7e4/22ec/811316_xlarge.png?m=1778739851", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f7e4/22ec/811316_xxlarge.png?m=1778739851", "created": 1778643039, "last_modified": 1778739851, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "FrankAdler", "last_touched": 1780568487, "title": "大家现在个人服务器一般怎么管理比较合适？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1217789", "created": 1780538003, "deleted": 0, "content": "我最近靠着 AI 辅助写了一些小项目，想部署到自己的服务器上跑起来。\r\n\r\n原本想着装个管理面板会省事很多，因为 ai 也这么推荐我操作来着，毕竟改 Nginx 配置、看日志、管理数据库、上传文件这些都有图形界面，对我这种新手运维可能比较友好。但后来翻了一些帖子，发现很多人对面板比较谨慎，原因大多是权限太高、暴露面变大，万一面板本身出问题，整台机器都可能受影响，而且我也害怕面板偷偷在背后把我服务器的东西传输出去。\r\n\r\n所以现在有点纠结了，对于像我这种新手运维来说，管理服务器是用面板还是用什么其他方法啊！", "content_rendered": "<p>我最近靠着 AI 辅助写了一些小项目，想部署到自己的服务器上跑起来。</p>\n<p>原本想着装个管理面板会省事很多，因为 ai 也这么推荐我操作来着，毕竟改 Nginx 配置、看日志、管理数据库、上传文件这些都有图形界面，对我这种新手运维可能比较友好。但后来翻了一些帖子，发现很多人对面板比较谨慎，原因大多是权限太高、暴露面变大，万一面板本身出问题，整台机器都可能受影响，而且我也害怕面板偷偷在背后把我服务器的东西传输出去。</p>\n<p>所以现在有点纠结了，对于像我这种新手运维来说，管理服务器是用面板还是用什么其他方法啊！</p>\n", "last_modified": 1780538003, "replies": 86, "id": 1217789}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1733731195", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1733731195", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 71391, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1733731195", "stars": 9701, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 434592, "username": "lynn1su", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/lynn1su", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f59f/474b/434592_mini.png?m=1777788899", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f59f/474b/434592_normal.png?m=1777788899", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f59f/474b/434592_large.png?m=1777788899", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f59f/474b/434592_xlarge.png?m=1777788899", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f59f/474b/434592_xxlarge.png?m=1777788899", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f59f/474b/434592_xxxlarge.png?m=1777788899", "created": 1565250257, "last_modified": 1777788899, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "lifechan", "last_touched": 1780569485, "title": "兄弟们， 5 月总计用了多少 token？我用了 34 亿，做了 3 个项目，主用 deepseek v4 pro", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1217791", "created": 1780538165, "deleted": 0, "content": "https://i.imgur.com/EhbDnE2.png", "content_rendered": "<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/EhbDnE2.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/EhbDnE2.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a>", "last_modified": 1780538165, "replies": 73, "id": 1217791}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a51f/b975/1298_large.png?m=1768486840", "name": "app", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a51f/b975/1298_normal.png?m=1768486840", "title": "App推荐", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/app", "topics": 16, "footer": "", "header": "别让好 App 埋没｜发你正在用的宝藏工具，顺便说清“为什么好用”", "title_alternative": "App推荐", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a51f/b975/1298_mini.png?m=1768486840", "stars": 8, "founder_id": 6746, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1298, "parent_node_name": null}, "member": {"id": 236252, "username": "JakeLaoyu", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/JakeLaoyu", "website": "https://github.com/JakeLaoyu", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/12f817e9e305db9283ad4d21c2de825e?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/12f817e9e305db9283ad4d21c2de825e?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/12f817e9e305db9283ad4d21c2de825e?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1497883273, "last_modified": 1780507473, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "JakeLaoyu", "last_touched": 1780561621, "title": "[自荐] 做了个纯 SSH 的服务器管理 App —— Caret,iOS 已上线", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1217750", "created": 1780507529, "deleted": 0, "content": "分享个自己做的小工具 Caret:用手机或 Mac,纯标准 SSH 管 Linux 服务器,服务器端零安装。\r\n\r\n能干啥:\r\n\r\n完整 SSH 终端(xterm,能跑 vim/htop/tail -f,多标签、断线重连、命令片段)\r\n\r\n实时监控:CPU/内存/磁盘/网络/负载 曲线,多机聚合一屏\r\n\r\nDocker 管理、Pod 部署模板、SFTP 文件传输\r\n\r\n隐私(最想强调的): 纯客户端,没有我的服务器,流量直达你的机器、不上报遥测;凭据只进系统 \r\nKeychain/Keystore;同步可选,走你自己的 iCloud / Google Drive(Drive 上端到端加密)。\r\n\r\niOS 已上线 App Store,免费下载; Android / macOS 即将跟上。\r\n\r\nApp Store: https://apps.apple.com/app/id6775111587 **没有上架中国区**\r\n\r\n介绍页: https://zobubo.com/products/caret\r\n\r\n附上永久高级版兑换码，在 app store 中兑换，app 中没有兑换入口\r\n\r\nXPKJR8WH6NLXTKA6EK\r\n\r\n47TXLXFLFNW8P3F4K8\r\n\r\n7YEMA6YAP4MX64EEE7\r\n\r\nPXX3LW3M47K3KPJJK8\r\n\r\nXJKXYHYE64AJJ7N4FH\r\n\r\nMPNK8AYL3HYRH87AHA\r\n\r\nWN6KERWEA4E87KHAEE\r\n\r\n8TPPMXF47HM6N776RP\r\n\r\nMNJHKJR4RHA6XYRXK6\r\n\r\nR6LPNEEXWFY36KR4HF\r\n\r\n6L8M3K8J68Y7PR443K\r\n\r\nHTNP6JKNJPJ3P74JFY\r\n\r\nPEHAA86YHFYMFHEAFT\r\n\r\n6MPMEKW6N3PYHLXMWN\r\n\r\n88TWAFTJWPE7E4AYTH\r\n\r\n3AMHW3RFE8PMF86PKR\r\n\r\nF6NMEMW33KFATJ7XL6\r\n\r\n7EAMFELH4A8HY4W4T3\r\n\r\nNKWPN6RJNHNW6M7X8F\r\n\r\nRR678KRLXRYALKXEA6\r\n\r\n\r\n接受好评，也接受反馈", "content_rendered": "<p>分享个自己做的小工具 Caret:用手机或 Mac,纯标准 SSH 管 Linux 服务器,服务器端零安装。</p>\n<p>能干啥:</p>\n<p>完整 SSH 终端(xterm,能跑 vim/htop/tail -f,多标签、断线重连、命令片段)</p>\n<p>实时监控:CPU/内存/磁盘/网络/负载 曲线,多机聚合一屏</p>\n<p>Docker 管理、Pod 部署模板、SFTP 文件传输</p>\n<p>隐私(最想强调的): 纯客户端,没有我的服务器,流量直达你的机器、不上报遥测;凭据只进系统\nKeychain/Keystore;同步可选,走你自己的 iCloud / Google Drive(Drive 上端到端加密)。</p>\n<p>iOS 已上线 App Store,免费下载; Android / macOS 即将跟上。</p>\n<p>App Store: <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/app/id6775111587\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://apps.apple.com/app/id6775111587</a> <strong>没有上架中国区</strong></p>\n<p>介绍页: <a href=\"https://zobubo.com/products/caret\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://zobubo.com/products/caret</a></p>\n<p>附上永久高级版兑换码，在 app store 中兑换，app 中没有兑换入口</p>\n<p>XPKJR8WH6NLXTKA6EK</p>\n<p>47TXLXFLFNW8P3F4K8</p>\n<p>7YEMA6YAP4MX64EEE7</p>\n<p>PXX3LW3M47K3KPJJK8</p>\n<p>XJKXYHYE64AJJ7N4FH</p>\n<p>MPNK8AYL3HYRH87AHA</p>\n<p>WN6KERWEA4E87KHAEE</p>\n<p>8TPPMXF47HM6N776RP</p>\n<p>MNJHKJR4RHA6XYRXK6</p>\n<p>R6LPNEEXWFY36KR4HF</p>\n<p>6L8M3K8J68Y7PR443K</p>\n<p>HTNP6JKNJPJ3P74JFY</p>\n<p>PEHAA86YHFYMFHEAFT</p>\n<p>6MPMEKW6N3PYHLXMWN</p>\n<p>88TWAFTJWPE7E4AYTH</p>\n<p>3AMHW3RFE8PMF86PKR</p>\n<p>F6NMEMW33KFATJ7XL6</p>\n<p>7EAMFELH4A8HY4W4T3</p>\n<p>NKWPN6RJNHNW6M7X8F</p>\n<p>RR678KRLXRYALKXEA6</p>\n<p>接受好评，也接受反馈</p>\n", "last_modified": 1780507710, "replies": 66, "id": 1217750}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1747623425", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1747623425", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 10982, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1747623425", "stars": 2346, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 406045, "username": "0xnycth", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/0xnycth", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4ee2/21b4/406045_mini.png?m=1658197092", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4ee2/21b4/406045_normal.png?m=1658197092", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4ee2/21b4/406045_large.png?m=1658197092", "created": 1556173529, "last_modified": 1658197092, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "yigedala", "last_touched": 1780495211, "title": "网上聊了个总裁助理的相亲对象，刚聊了几句，问了个问题，她就毛了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1217714", "created": 1780494076, "deleted": 0, "content": "内容前面无非就是寒暄，晚上好啥的。\r\n然后我看到她的资料写的总裁助理。\r\n\r\n我就说：你做总裁助理的啊，好厉害\r\n\r\n她回：有什么厉害的，也是搬砖\r\n\r\n我说：那不是离权力中心很近吗\r\n\r\n她回：没啥用\r\n\r\n我说：哈哈哈为啥啊，我也不太懂这个\r\n\r\n她回：没事，也没那么多为啥\r\n\r\n————这时候我看她好像不想聊工作，我就看他学历是 985/211\r\n\r\n我说：你学历好高啊，学霸来的\r\n\r\n她回：你在考虑什么\r\n\r\n我回：啊？就聊天啊，学历咋了吗\r\n\r\n——————\r\n\r\n然后就没有任何回复了。\r\n\r\n奇怪的人真多啊。", "content_rendered": "<p>内容前面无非就是寒暄，晚上好啥的。\n然后我看到她的资料写的总裁助理。</p>\n<p>我就说：你做总裁助理的啊，好厉害</p>\n<p>她回：有什么厉害的，也是搬砖</p>\n<p>我说：那不是离权力中心很近吗</p>\n<p>她回：没啥用</p>\n<p>我说：哈哈哈为啥啊，我也不太懂这个</p>\n<p>她回：没事，也没那么多为啥</p>\n<p>————这时候我看她好像不想聊工作，我就看他学历是 985/211</p>\n<p>我说：你学历好高啊，学霸来的</p>\n<p>她回：你在考虑什么</p>\n<p>我回：啊？就聊天啊，学历咋了吗</p>\n<p>——————</p>\n<p>然后就没有任何回复了。</p>\n<p>奇怪的人真多啊。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1780494076, "replies": 64, "id": 1217714}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9a11/5815/52_large.png?m=1630576655", "name": "hardware", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9a11/5815/52_normal.png?m=1630576655", "title": "硬件", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/hardwa